data.description: This lovely home boasts four bedrooms and the lower level has been transformed into a beautiful additional bedroom. Features fully paid-off Solar. As you explore the house, you'll find spacious rooms designed to spark creativity, along with a luxurious four-car garage. Perfect for entertaining, the home's layout flows seamlessly, creating an open and inviting atmosphere.    Inside, you'll discover a comfortable living area and a welcoming great room. The kitchen is a culinary haven, with plenty of cabinets and counter space, connecting effortlessly to the dining area and great room, offering delightful backyard views. Just past the kitchen, the imaginative seller has added an extra room, currently used as a bedroom, with a charming rustic theme and a unique barn door.    The laundry area has its own space, complete with a peaceful soaking sink and cabinets for storage. Upstairs, there's a spacious landing that can be transformed into an office, a cozy retreat, a game room, or whatever suits your fancy. Two bedrooms at the end of the hallway enjoy their private full bath with dual sinks and a tub/shower combo.    The master suite is a grand space with a retreat area perfect for a nursery, library, gym, yoga corner, or glamorous beauty station. The master bath features a separate shower, a luxurious tub, and a dual sink counter. The home has been updated considerately with a RainSoft triple-filter water purifier and a fully owned solar system, ensuring smart financial choices.    Step into the enchanting backyard, enclosed by a fully fenced perimeter, inviting families with kids and pets to enjoy its embrace. Take a personalized tour of this extraordinary home—schedule your private showing today and immerse yourself in the captivating charm it offers.
